@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Homework 4</h1>
    <p class="lead">This assignment is to get us familiar with ASP.NET MVC 5, GET, POST, and other important development tools.
    More info can be found by clicking the button below. In this homework I will be creating a Metric Converter and a Color Chooser.
    At this moment I am not sure how that is going to happen, but eventually I will get it down.</p>
    <p><a href="http://www.wou.edu/~morses/classes/cs46x/assignments/HW4_1819.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
